header.gameNote: New York Life ACC Tournament - Final

videos.description: Jordan Usher sends a beautiful bounce pass to Moses Wright, who finishes with a two-handed flush.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wright dunks one down with authority early for Georgia Tech) 2021/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wright dunks one down with authority early for Georgia Tech

videos.description: Dan Shulman touts the above-the-rim camera and right on cue Anthony Polite scores the tough alley-oop layup plus a foul for Florida State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (FSU's alley-oop looks nice on the above-the-rim cam) 2021/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: FSU's alley-oop looks nice on the above-the-rim cam

videos.description: Allison Williams reveals Georgia Tech head coach Josh Pastner's voicemail message, which has many words of wisdom.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Misc. (Pastner's voicemail message is quite motivational) 2021/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pastner's voicemail message is quite motivational

videos.description: Georgia Tech forces a turnover, then Michael Devoe leads Jose Alvarado with a bounce pass for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Devoe sends a long pass ahead to Alvarado for a layup) 2021/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Devoe sends a long pass ahead to Alvarado for a layup

videos.description: Malik Osborne makes the extra pass to set up Tanor Ngom's dunk, then Georgia Tech answers with a Moses Wright and-1 slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ngom, Wright trade dunks in second half) 2021/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ngom, Wright trade dunks in second half

videos.description: Scottie Barnes blows by his defender and lays one in for Florida State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Barnes weaves through for an acrobatic layup) 2021/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Barnes weaves through for an acrobatic layup

videos.description: Jordan Usher gets free with a pump-fake, then drives in and throws down a big slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Usher shows no mercy with this huge Georgia Tech dunk) 2021/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Usher shows no mercy with this huge Georgia Tech dunk

videos.description: Jose Alvarado makes another great defensive play to set up Michael Devoe's layup, but the bench swarms the court with 0.6 seconds on the clock.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Georgia Tech storms court slightly premature of ACC tourney title) 2021/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia Tech storms court slightly premature of ACC tourney title
